{"tid":1185284,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【狂徒再現】龍運巴士座位插針筒拮傷女乘客 重案組接手調查","createTime":"2019-06-04T07:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T09:21:22.000Z","uid":15660,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"22855750d761d3d774a955fe3c98a386fee12036","tid":1185284,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"【12:22】新增龍運巴士回應<br />\n【11:14】大嶼山警區重案組接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n東涌逸東邨巴士總站，早上8時45分，一名年約30歲女乘客乘搭龍運巴士S64X路線，在上層左邊後五排位置，其間被前面座位伸出的一支針筒，拮傷左小腿，女車長代為報警求助，女乘客送院治理，大嶼山警區重案組接手調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息表示，針筒是一般醫療用、針身較細小的類型，被藏在座椅背與座位間隙縫，針嘴伸出，女乘客上車坐在上層左邊後五排近窗的座椅，當時她未有為意「陷阱」，其間「伸腳」，便被前面座椅插住的針筒嘴拮傷，她向車長求助，由車長代為報警。<br />\n<br />\n龍運發言人回應事件時表示，今早約9時，一輛S64X線龍運巴士在駛至逸東邨總站時，車長接獲一名女乘客指在車廂內被針筒刺傷，車長報警處理，乘客送院治理，龍運已派員慰問傷者。<br />\n<br />\n龍運對事件表示關注，並強烈譴責任何企圖傷害乘客的行為。龍運會配合警方調查，並要求前線同事加強車廂檢查，呼籲乘客除了察看自己的座位，亦應留意身邊的座位有否可疑物件，以及可疑人士，若有發現，應立即報警及通知車長處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190604/59674413?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190604%2F59674413%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CglNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=33545ab7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190604%2F59674413%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&h=e9216f73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190604/59674413?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link</a>"},{"pid":"9c52b7aefaddd69ea97a5f17ff2a9212fe2a775f","tid":1185284,"uid":105775,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"@N賓 認左罪未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a12c079d11f5e010d6c7e40d2b404ecf12b18c9","tid":1185284,"uid":23779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:36:05.000Z","msg":"牙賓又出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c362d44b76c3c3cd61a68f64d834c3e940e7229","tid":1185284,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:37:08.000Z","msg":"n賓翻起愛恨～"},{"pid":"2601eed592c999e62b393516d713c5d60330fac0","tid":1185284,"uid":124891,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:37:30.000Z","msg":"咪屈 佢放開觀塘區"},{"pid":"3353f0d19903054d287730ef9b9fa6095eda25a1","tid":1185284,"uid":115245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T07:53:59.000Z","msg":"N賓收手啦"},{"pid":"e21a5582891bd5a83b399ff5629bcb635e5d72e1","tid":1185284,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"留意幾號綫"},{"pid":"8ab448dfbad20afaa3ed2a662f8fe960df733f1e","tid":1185284,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:20:16.000Z","msg":"剛剛石壁放監<br />\n又作案"},{"pid":"7eefe82901904d78fdb11e51547c9c0791aac684","tid":1185284,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T09:21:22.000Z","msg":"NBxx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}